Human Resource Manager - Global Media Agency - Dubai Based
Very competitive salary
(up to GBP 42,000) - Tax Free + Bennefits
Shortlist
Add to shortlist
Looking for Human Resource Manager to work in a global media agency based in Dubai.
The candidate must be currently working in HR and must have a minimum of 5 years of experience.
HR in media is a plus, but profiles coming from other sectors will also be considered.
The candidate must be perfectly fluent in English. Arabic speaking in a great plus.
Very competitive salary + standard relocation package (Visa, Health Insurance, Flights).
Working for one of the biggest media conglomerates in the region with amazing career development opportunities.
